snippet: New recordings are available from Dom La Nena, Wooden Wand, Broadcast, Katie Armiger, Mystical Weapons, and Pantha du Prince and the Bell Laboratory.
abstract: Jon Pareles reviews new recordings by singer Dom La Nena, Southern-rock performer Wooden Wand, electronica group Broadcast, country singer Katie Armiger, studio duo Mystical Weapons and electronic musician Pantha du Prince with Norwegian collective the Bell Laboratory.
lead_paragraph: New recordings are available from Dom La Nena, Wooden Wand, Broadcast, Katie Armiger, Mystical Weapons, and Pantha du Prince and the Bell Laboratory.
